{"tid":1643569,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"提早收舖公司點計你地份人工","createTime":"2019-10-10T07:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T08:51:25.000Z","uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c981b865c0f58369bd523a70e1946a8b2233e4a2","tid":1643569,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"我因為想高人工而轉呢份工（做sales)<br />\n大西北出到 港島九龍<br />\n一日都有最少55蚊車<br />\n我都係安排收夜班<br />\n所以連續幾日都離落閘返咗兩三個鐘<br />\n今個月出人工法國公司淨係計咗我返工時間<br />\ncut哂 落閘之後嘅人工<br />\n變相低過我之前份工扣埋車費同ot 等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我支持黃c<br />\n但我覺得公司真係好度<br />\n隔離店出足人工當嗰日全日返足只係冇佣金單計。<br />\n<br />\n我諗呢個情況都會持續<br />\n想搵間公司係會出足人工就算落閘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5518e219429b9b3129f6802804cb025a7c66af5c","tid":1643569,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9d1825211c231eec6e3133ceb07c515659466942","tid":1643569,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:47:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ad4ebfe83c31abd6228a82691f623c7a012eef6","tid":1643569,"uid":210434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"直接當收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後要補鐘或者當放例假"},{"pid":"39a4491303a68dcf9f96a21a7d80404442026b35","tid":1643569,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"時間車費付出左<br />\n班黃c咁理性係度唱下歌<br />\n落閘係公司決定<br />\n一蚊都唔俾番真係好過份<br />\n<br />\n我返屋企用足3h<br />\n剩係遲左3分鐘鬧到我好似欠咗佢哋咁<br />\n。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想轉工"},{"pid":"a6d664ec8f9c42fc3e841476473e1bb034e151a0","tid":1643569,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:51:25.000Z","